{
  "texts": [
    "While this might be less biased, it would also be more time-consuming.",
    "It might also be impossible to get certain first-hand information (e.g.",
    "protocols of past meetings of the board of directors).",
    "It is worth noting that not all company information is equally biased.",
    "For example, while reports by management might be too positive, whistleblower reports might be too negative."
  ]
}